OL,3,CLondon councils 'biggest losers' under
OL,4,Cgovernment plans to change funding
OL,6,FLondon councils will be the biggest
OL,7,Flosers under government plans to
OL,8,Fchange funding, according to a report.
OL,10,FThe Institute for Fiscal Studies found
OL,11,Fsome London boroughs could see funding
OL,12,Fdrop up to 12% once inflation is taken
OL,13,Finto account.
OL,15,FThe changes will mean they will have
OL,16,Fless money to spend on services even
OL,17,Fif council taxes are increased.
OL,19,FOverall cash for inner London town
OL,20,Fhalls would be 11 to 12 per cent lower
OL,21,Fin 2028/29 in real terms.
