OL,3,CLondon councils 'biggest losers' under
OL,4,Cgovernment plans to change funding
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer's own council, Camden
OL,7,Fin north London, will be hit by the
OL,8,Freforms when taking inflation into
OL,9,Faccount, the IFS added.
OL,11,FThe think tank said Camden, along with
OL,12,Fother inner London boroughs including
OL,13,FWestminster, will have less money to
OL,14,Fspend on services even if they
OL,15,Fincrease council tax by the maximum
OL,16,Famount allowed.
