OL,3,CLondon councils 'biggest losers' under
OL,4,Cgovernment plans to change funding
OL,6,FWhitehall will provide a minimum level
OL,7,Fof funding, a so-called funding floor,
OL,8,Ffor council leaders during the
OL,9,Fchanges, but the IFS said overall cash
OL,10,Ffor inner London town halls would be
OL,11,Flower in 2028-29 in real terms.
OL,13,FThe paper said: "Around one in four
OL,14,Fcouncils would see real-terms falls in
OL,15,Foverall funding under the Government's
OL,16,Fproposals, with around 30 on the
OL,17,Flowest funding floors seeing real-
OL,18,Fterms cuts of 11`12%. Conversely,
OL,19,Fanother one in four councils would see
OL,20,Freal-terms increases of 12% or more."
