OL,3,CLondon councils 'biggest losers' under
OL,4,Cgovernment plans to change funding
OL,6,FThe overall Government spend on local
OL,7,Fauthorities will not change. The
OL,8,Fchanges will be phased in across three
OL,9,Fyears, from 2026/27 to 2028/29.
OL,11,FKate Ogden, co-author of the IFS
OL,12,Freport and a senior research economist
OL,13,Fwith the think tank, said: "England
OL,14,Fhas lacked a rational system of local
OL,15,Fgovernment funding for at least 12
OL,16,Fyears ` and arguably more like 20. It
OL,17,Fis therefore welcome that the nettle
OL,18,Fof funding reform is being grasped,
OL,19,Fand some councils will benefit
OL,20,Fsubstantially under the new system.
OL,26,@uD@\OU
