OL,3,CLondon councils 'biggest losers' under
OL,4,Cgovernment plans to change funding
OL,6,FThe report added: "It is somewhat
OL,7,Fsurprising that, on average, councils
OL,8,Fin the most deprived 30% of areas
OL,9,Fwould see very similar changes in
OL,10,Foverall funding over the next three
OL,11,Fyears to those for councils in the
OL,12,Fmiddle 40% of areas."
OL,14,FIt noted that rural areas, which
OL,15,Ffeared being badly hit by changes,
OL,16,Fwill benefit from a "remoteness
OL,17,Fadjustment" which will compensate
OL,18,Fareas with higher needs due to being
OL,19,Ffar from large towns.
