OL,3,CLondon councils 'biggest losers' under
OL,4,Cgovernment plans to change funding
OL,6,FOutside the capital, the East Midlands
OL,7,F(22%) and Yorkshire & the Humber (19%)
OL,8,Fare set to see the biggest increases
OL,9,Fin funding, with the South East set to
OL,10,Fsee the smallest at 13%.
OL,12,FHowever, the proposals have been
OL,13,Fcriticised by youth charity the
OL,14,FNational Children's Bureau, which said
OL,15,Fit was "significantly concerned" about
OL,16,Fthe way the Government plans to work
OL,17,Fout needs for children's services.
