OL,3,CLondon councils 'biggest losers' under
OL,4,Cgovernment plans to change funding
OL,6,FMs Ogden added: "The Government should
OL,7,Fconsider giving highly affected
OL,8,Fcouncils which currently have low
OL,9,Fcouncil tax rates greater flexibility
OL,10,Fto bring their council tax bills up to
OL,11,Fmore typical levels to offset funding
OL,12,Flosses.
OL,14,F"More generally, reform of council
OL,15,Ffunding allocations is just one part
OL,16,Fof the financial sustainability
OL,17,Fpuzzle. Efforts to reduce demands on,
OL,18,Fand the cost of providing, local
OL,19,Fservices through reform and the use of
OL,20,Fnew technology will also be vital."
