OL,3,CLondon councils 'biggest losers' under
OL,4,Cgovernment plans to change funding
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Ministry of
OL,7,FHousing, Communities and Local
OL,8,FGovernment said: "The current,
OL,9,Foutdated way in which local
OL,10,Fauthorities are funded means the link
OL,11,Fbetween funding and need for services
OL,12,Fhas broken down, leaving communities
OL,13,Fleft behind.
OL,15,F"That's why we are taking decisive
OL,16,Faction to reform the funding system so
OL,17,Fwe can get councils back on their feet
OL,18,Fand improve public services, with the
OL,19,FIFS recognising that our changes will
OL,20,Fbetter align funding with councils'
OL,21,Fneeds."
